==English==

===Etymology===
From [[dead]] and [[ice]]

===Noun===
'''dead ice'''
# Former [[glacier]] ice that is not longer connected to the active glacier, therefore not moving anymore and getting covered with [[sediment]]s.

====Synonyms====
*[[stagnant ice]]

